<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BRAINROT WORLD — Game Design Document</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Russo+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --neon: #00ffcc;
    --hot: #ff2d55;
    --gold: #ffd700;
    --purple: #9b30ff;
    --bg: #060610;
    --card: #0d0d22;
    --text: #e8e8ff;
    --dim: #6666aa;
  }

- { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: var(–bg);
color: var(–text);
font-family: ‘Space Mono’, monospace;
overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* animated grid bg */
body::before {
content: ‘’;
position: fixed; inset: 0;
background-image:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,204,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,204,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 40px 40px;
z-index: 0;
animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes gridMove {
0% { background-position: 0 0; }
100% { background-position: 40px 40px; }
}

.container { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }

/* HERO */
.hero {
text-align: center;
padding: 60px 20px 40px;
position: relative;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
font-family: ‘Space Mono’, monospace;
font-size: 11px;
letter-spacing: 6px;
color: var(–neon);
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 16px;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.2s;
}
.hero-title {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(64px, 14vw, 140px);
line-height: 0.9;
letter-spacing: 4px;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, var(–neon) 60%, var(–hot) 100%);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
background-clip: text;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.4s;
}
.hero-sub {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 48px);
color: var(–gold);
letter-spacing: 8px;
margin-top: 8px;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.6s;
}
.hero-desc {
margin-top: 24px;
font-size: 13px;
color: var(–dim);
max-width: 500px;
margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
line-height: 1.8;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.8s;
}
.badge-row {
display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
margin-top: 24px;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 1s;
}
.badge {
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.08);
border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.3);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 6px 16px;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–neon);
letter-spacing: 2px;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* SECTIONS */
.section {
margin: 48px 0;
opacity: 0;
transform: translateY(30px);
transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
}
.section.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

.section-header {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.section-num {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 48px;
color: rgba(0,255,204,0.15);
line-height: 1;
min-width: 50px;
}
.section-title {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 32px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
color: #fff;
}
.section-line {
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,204,0.4), transparent);
}

/* CARDS */
.card-grid { display: grid; gap: 16px; }
.card-grid.cols-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); }
.card-grid.cols-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); }

.card {
background: var(–card);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 24px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
cursor: default;
}
.card:hover {
transform: translateY(-4px);
border-color: rgba(0,255,204,0.3);
}
.card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
background: var(–card-accent, var(–neon));
opacity: 0.6;
}
.card-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.card-title {
font-family: ‘Russo One’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 8px;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.card-text {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–dim);
line-height: 1.8;
}
.card-tag {
display: inline-block;
margin-top: 12px;
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.1);
color: var(–neon);
border-radius: 4px;
padding: 3px 10px;
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
}

/* LOOP DIAGRAM */
.loop {
background: var(–card);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 32px;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.loop-steps {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
}
.loop-step {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
gap: 8px; text-align: center;
padding: 16px;
min-width: 120px;
}
.loop-icon {
width: 56px; height: 56px;
border-radius: 50%;
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
font-size: 24px;
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.08);
border: 2px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.2);
transition: all 0.3s;
}
.loop-step:hover .loop-icon {
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.2);
border-color: var(–neon);
transform: scale(1.1);
}
.loop-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(–dim); letter-spacing: 1px; max-width: 90px; line-height: 1.5; }
.loop-arrow { font-size: 20px; color: rgba(0,255,204,0.3); padding: 0 4px; }

/* MONSTERS */
.monster-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
.monster-card {
background: var(–card);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 20px 16px;
text-align: center;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
transition: all 0.25s;
cursor: pointer;
position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.monster-card:hover {
border-color: var(–hot);
transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.02);
box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255,45,85,0.15);
}
.monster-card::after {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; inset: 0;
background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,45,85,0.12), transparent 70%);
opacity: 0;
transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.monster-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

.monster-sprite {
font-size: 52px;
display: block;
margin-bottom: 10px;
animation: bobble 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes bobble {
0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
}
.monster-card:nth-child(2) .monster-sprite { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
.monster-card:nth-child(3) .monster-sprite { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
.monster-card:nth-child(4) .monster-sprite { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
.monster-card:nth-child(5) .monster-sprite { animation-delay: 1.6s; }
.monster-card:nth-child(6) .monster-sprite { animation-delay: 2s; }

.monster-name {
font-family: ‘Russo One’, sans-serif;
font-size: 12px;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.monster-type {
font-size: 10px;
color: var(–dim);
letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.rarity {
display: inline-block;
margin-top: 8px;
padding: 2px 8px;
border-radius: 4px;
font-size: 9px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
font-weight: 700;
}
.rarity.common { background: rgba(150,150,150,0.2); color: #aaa; }
.rarity.rare { background: rgba(30,144,255,0.2); color: #4da6ff; }
.rarity.epic { background: rgba(155,48,255,0.2); color: #c66fff; }
.rarity.legendary { background: rgba(255,215,0,0.2); color: var(–gold); }

/* MAP */
.map-visual {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628, #0d0d22);
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 32px;
border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.1);
position: relative;
min-height: 260px;
overflow: hidden;
}
.map-visual::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; inset: 0;
background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,255,204,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 28px 28px;
}
.map-nodes {
position: relative; z-index: 1;
display: flex; align-items: center;
flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0;
justify-content: space-around;
padding: 20px 0;
}
.map-node {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
position: relative;
}
.node-circle {
width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%;
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
font-size: 22px;
position: relative;
transition: all 0.3s;
cursor: pointer;
}
.node-circle.active {
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.15);
border: 2px solid var(–neon);
box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,204,0.3), 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,204,0.1);
animation: pulse-node 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.node-circle.battle {
background: rgba(255,45,85,0.15);
border: 2px solid var(–hot);
box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,45,85,0.3);
}
.node-circle.shop {
background: rgba(255,215,0,0.15);
border: 2px solid var(–gold);
}
.node-circle.boss {
background: rgba(155,48,255,0.15);
border: 2px solid var(–purple);
box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(155,48,255,0.4);
animation: pulse-boss 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse-node {
0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,204,0.3); }
50% { box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(0,255,204,0.6); }
}
@keyframes pulse-boss {
0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(155,48,255,0.4); }
50% { box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(155,48,255,0.8); }
}
.node-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(–dim); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; max-width: 70px; }
.path-line {
flex: 1; min-width: 40px; height: 2px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,204,0.2), rgba(0,255,204,0.1));
position: relative; margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.path-line::after {
content: ‘▶’;
position: absolute; right: -6px; top: -7px;
font-size: 10px; color: rgba(0,255,204,0.3);
}

/* MONETIZATION */
.money-card { –card-accent: var(–gold); }
.money-card .card-title { color: var(–gold); }
.money-card .card-tag { background: rgba(255,215,0,0.1); color: var(–gold); }

/* CATCH MECHANIC */
.catch-steps {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
gap: 16px;
}
.catch-step {
background: var(–card);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 20px;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
position: relative;
}
.step-num {
position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px;
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 32px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}
.catch-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.catch-title {
font-family: ‘Russo One’, sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.catch-text { font-size: 11px; color: var(–dim); line-height: 1.7; }

/* LOCA TABS */
.loca-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.loca-tab {
padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 8px;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
background: transparent; color: var(–dim);
font-family: ‘Space Mono’, monospace; font-size: 12px;
cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.loca-tab.active, .loca-tab:hover {
background: rgba(0,255,204,0.1);
border-color: var(–neon);
color: var(–neon);
}
.loca-content {
background: var(–card);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 24px;
border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,204,0.15);
}
.loca-name {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 3px;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.loca-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(–dim); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.loca-stats { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.loca-stat { }
.loca-stat-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(–dim); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
.loca-stat-val {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 22px; color: var(–neon);
letter-spacing: 2px;
}

/* TIMELINE */
.timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
.timeline::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; left: 8px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
width: 2px;
background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(–neon), var(–purple), var(–hot));
opacity: 0.3;
}
.tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.tl-dot {
position: absolute; left: -28px; top: 4px;
width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
background: var(–neon);
box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(–neon);
}
.tl-phase {
font-size: 10px; color: var(–neon); letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.tl-title {
font-family: ‘Russo One’, sans-serif;
font-size: 15px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.tl-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(–dim); line-height: 1.7; }

/* FOOTER */
footer {
text-align: center;
padding: 48px 20px;
border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
margin-top: 60px;
}
footer p { font-size: 11px; color: var(–dim); letter-spacing: 3px; }

/* SCROLLBAR */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(–bg); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,255,204,0.3); border-radius: 3px; }

/* DIVIDER */
.divider {
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0,255,204,0.15), transparent);
margin: 40px 0;
}

/* highlight */
.hl { color: var(–neon); }
.hl-hot { color: var(–hot); }
.hl-gold { color: var(–gold); }
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- HERO -->

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Game Design Document v1.0</div>
    <div class="hero-title">BRAINROT<br>WORLD</div>
    <div class="hero-sub">Catch · Battle · Dominate</div>
    <div class="hero-desc">
      Геолокационная онлайн-игра с ловлей Italian Brainrot монстров, PvP-битвами на реальной карте и глубокой системой прогрессии.
    </div>
    <div class="badge-row">
      <span class="badge">iOS / Android</span>
      <span class="badge">Онлайн PvP</span>
      <span class="badge">Геолокация</span>
      <span class="badge">Catch & Battle</span>
      <span class="badge">F2P + Premium</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- CORE CONCEPT -->

  <div class="section" id="s1">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">01</div>
      <div class="section-title">CORE CONCEPT</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="loop">
      <div class="loop-steps">
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">🗺️</div>
          <div class="loop-label">Ходишь по реальной карте</div>
        </div>
        <div class="loop-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">👾</div>
          <div class="loop-label">Встречаешь Brainrot монстра</div>
        </div>
        <div class="loop-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">🎯</div>
          <div class="loop-label">Мини-игра на поимку</div>
        </div>
        <div class="loop-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">⚔️</div>
          <div class="loop-label">PvP в точке встречи</div>
        </div>
        <div class="loop-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">📈</div>
          <div class="loop-label">Качаешь монстра, берёшь лут</div>
        </div>
        <div class="loop-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="loop-step">
          <div class="loop-icon">🏆</div>
          <div class="loop-label">Захватываешь локации</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MAP & NODES -->

  <div class="section" id="s2">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">02</div>
      <div class="section-title">КАРТА И УЗЛЫ</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="map-visual">
      <div class="map-nodes">
        <div class="map-node">
          <div class="node-circle active">🏠</div>
          <div class="node-label">Точка спавна</div>
        </div>
        <div class="path-line"></div>
        <div class="map-node">
          <div class="node-circle battle">⚔️</div>
          <div class="node-label">PvP Арена</div>
        </div>
        <div class="path-line"></div>
        <div class="map-node">
          <div class="node-circle active">👾</div>
          <div class="node-label">Спавн монстров</div>
        </div>
        <div class="path-line"></div>
        <div class="map-node">
          <div class="node-circle shop">🛒</div>
          <div class="node-label">Магазин</div>
        </div>
        <div class="path-line"></div>
        <div class="map-node">
          <div class="node-circle boss">💀</div>
          <div class="node-label">Босс-локация</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:16px" class="card-grid cols-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📍</div>
        <div class="card-title">Точки спавна</div>
        <div class="card-text">Монстры появляются на реальных точках карты: парки, торговые центры, перекрёстки. Привязаны к типу местности — редкие в центре города, обычные везде.</div>
        <span class="card-tag">DYNAMIC SPAWN</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">⚔️</div>
        <div class="card-title">PvP Арены</div>
        <div class="card-text">Два игрока оказываются в одной точке → автоматически предлагается дуэль. 3 монстра против 3. Победитель получает очки территории и лут проигравшего.</div>
        <span class="card-tag">AUTO-TRIGGER</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🏰</div>
        <div class="card-title">Захват локаций</div>
        <div class="card-text">Реальные POI-точки можно захватить командой. Захваченная точка даёт пассивный доход BrainCoins каждые 30 минут, пока её не отобьют.</div>
        <span class="card-tag">TERRITORY CONTROL</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LOCAS -->

  <div class="section" id="s3">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">03</div>
      <div class="section-title">ЛОКАЦИИ (LOCA)</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="loca-tabs">
      <button class="loca-tab active" onclick="showLoca(0)">ROMA SLUMS</button>
      <button class="loca-tab" onclick="showLoca(1)">COLOSSEO</button>
      <button class="loca-tab" onclick="showLoca(2)">SICILIAN VOID</button>
      <button class="loca-tab" onclick="showLoca(3)">VENICE SWAMP</button>
      <button class="loca-tab" onclick="showLoca(4)">NAPOLI CHAOS</button>
    </div>
    <div class="loca-content" id="locaBox">
      <div class="loca-name" style="color: var(--neon)">🏚️ ROMA SLUMS</div>
      <div class="loca-desc">Стартовая локация. Узкие улочки, граффити, монстры среднего уровня. Идеальна для обучения механикам. Здесь спавнится Tung Tung Sahur и его братья-пеньки.</div>
      <div class="loca-stats">
        <div class="loca-stat"><div class="loca-stat-label">Время</div><div class="loca-stat-val">3 МИН</div></div>
        <div class="loca-stat"><div class="loca-stat-label">Монстры</div><div class="loca-stat-val">12+</div></div>
        <div class="loca-stat"><div class="loca-stat-label">Уровень</div><div class="loca-stat-val">1–10</div></div>
        <div class="loca-stat"><div class="loca-stat-label">Игроки</div><div class="loca-stat-val">∞</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MONSTERS -->

  <div class="section" id="s4">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">04</div>
      <div class="section-title">ITALIAN BRAINROT — ROSTER</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="monster-grid">
      <div class="monster-card">
        <span class="monster-sprite">🪵</span>
        <div class="monster-name">TUNG TUNG SAHUR</div>
